code: @Override public ParsedLine parse(String line, int cursor, ParseContext context) {     if (!line.trim().endsWith(EOF_CHARACTER) && context != ParseContext.COMPLETE) {         throw new EOFError(-1, -1, "New line without EOF character.", NEW_LINE_PROMPT).     }     final ArgumentList parsedLine = (ArgumentList) super.parse(line, cursor, context).     return new SqlArgumentList(parsedLine.line(), parsedLine.words(), parsedLine.wordIndex(), parsedLine.wordCursor(), parsedLine.cursor(), null, parsedLine.rawWordCursor(), parsedLine.rawWordLength()). }
@Override public CharSequence escape(CharSequence candidate, boolean complete) {     // e.g. 'INS(ERT INTO)' should not be quoted but 'SELECT * FROM T(axi Rides)' should     return candidate. }
